body:
### Welcome to LJSES Feeds.
This will be feeds from the development team.

If you're using the GitHub for Mac, simply sync your repository and you'll see the new branch.

### Designer.
Leo Jackson(@lajjr) and the use of phonegap, jscript, google apis, github, HTML5, JQuery-Mobile.

### Where are the New Features?
Coming Soon due the clients and the requests this has been back burner for a loooooooong time.

### Authors and Contributors
The main Authors for this is Leo Jackson (@lajjr) John Mazer (@jmazer).

### Support or Contact
Submit errors to https://github.com/lajjr/ljsesfeed/issues and contact us contact@ljses.net .
